Yeah I get the impression there are several "gates/doors/windows" (its just a word used to describe)

  Since we are on the subject I looked a few up from the "library" to add to it. Not enough room to post them all but heres a few from over the years mentioning it. Quality and methods vary.
   
  Misty
Frank Ratka <warrior18eii@...> wrote: 
              Here are some I got on the gate also. Just to validate!

Regards,

Frank R.

  ----- Original Message ----
From: Frank Sumption <franks-boxes@...>
To: Group <evp-itc@yahoogroups.com>
Sent: Friday, January 18, 2008 2:48:58 PM
Subject: [EVP-ITC] More from EVPamker

    Figured as long as it's working----
 
 The image voice is cuz they give me images of how I supposedly look on their side. I always wonder if that's really what it's supposed to be. 
 
 I went back to 80ms, I like the voice quality better. 
 
 I got a kind of garbels voice form yesterday aobut eh gate working better in this region, maybe that's why EVPmaker works here, and not so much at home?
 
 Frank-S
